reportingResults_country Dataset

Source: R/data-specs.R
reportingResults_country.Rd

Usage

reportingResults_country

Format

A data frame with 432 rows and 10 columns:

GroupID

grouping variable

GroupLevel

level of grouping variable

Numerator

number of flags in group

Denominator

total subjects in group

Metric

calculated rate/metric value

Score

statistical score

Flag

ordinal flag to be applied

MetricID

unique metric identifier

StudyID

unique study identifier

SnapshotDate

date of the snapshot

Source

Generated from reportingResults_country.csv dataset in the gsm package.
